It was more he thought
it would improve his playing.

275
00:15:17,834 --> 00:15:20,603
You're fearless
if you use smack.

276
00:15:20,603 --> 00:15:22,305
You don't have any feelings.

277
00:15:22,305 --> 00:15:25,208
You're not scared of anybody
or anything.

278
00:15:25,208 --> 00:15:28,644
Whatever you wanted to play,
you played.

279
00:15:28,644 --> 00:15:30,480
It was just wonderful.

280
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:31,514
[Laughs]

281
00:15:31,514 --> 00:15:33,583
He didn't want to be
a family man

282
00:15:33,583 --> 00:15:36,119
Or anything like that,
