00:20:04,086 --> 00:20:06,156
* Playin' with an R&B band *

375
00:20:06,156 --> 00:20:07,423
* Oh, yeah! *

376
00:20:07,423 --> 00:20:09,559
His reputation was as being,
you know,

377
00:20:09,559 --> 00:20:12,328
Probably the best drummer around
in those days.

378
00:20:12,328 --> 00:20:15,465
It was really Ginger's
first taste of fame, yes.

379
00:20:15,465 --> 00:20:18,000
It's the same with you, Ginger.

380
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,302
This is beat.

381
00:20:19,302 --> 00:20:20,570
