00:21:50,493 --> 00:21:53,796
I wouldn't be playing
during his drum solo.

412
00:21:53,796 --> 00:21:57,900
And I off-loaded
a right-hander on him.

413
00:21:57,900 --> 00:22:01,504
He went down on the ground,
