00:26:21,764 --> 00:26:25,901
* I'll be with you,
darling, soon *

496
00:26:25,901 --> 00:26:30,773
* I'll be with you
when the stars start falling *

497
00:26:30,773 --> 00:26:34,977
* I've been waiting so long *

